## Current Project State

- Python 3.11 virtual environment (`.venv`) active with live-path dependencies installed.
- `src/` package scaffolded with ingestion, live analysis, recording, and bridge modules.
- Milestones 1 and 2 complete: full live pipeline from mic through aubio to virtual MIDI port, with YAML config, extended CLI, and diagnostics monitoring.
- Milestone 4 (Web UI) complete: FastAPI API layer (`src/api/`) with session management, REST endpoints, and WebSocket MIDI streaming; Next.js 16 frontend (`web/`) with device selector, record controls, and live piano-roll MIDI visualizer.
