## Known Blockers

- **aubio Python 3.11 wheels**: Use `aubio-ledfx` fork (upstream has no 3.11 wheels).
- **DDSP + Python 3.11**: TF compatibility issues. Resolved via subprocess isolation — DDSP runs in a dedicated Python 3.10 venv (`.venv-ddsp`), invoked as a subprocess from the main 3.11 app.
- **WaveNet/NSynth (Group 3)**: Training requires GPU and dataset of ≥500 isolated drum hits per class.
- **PyTorch + TF isolation**: Groups 2+3 (PyTorch, main process) and Group 1 DDSP (TF, subprocess) must never run in the same process.
